<plot>Akilah and Shaun have reached a crossroad in their relationship; he is ready to be intimate; she is not unless, they are both tested for HIV/AIDS. Affected:The AIDS Project, delves into the reasons why they are on opposite sides of the fence and how their encounters with those who are infected with HIV/AIDS have affected their views of the disease differently.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?024647</url></doc>
